                      ),
                    ),
                  ),
                ],
              ),
            ),
          ],
        ),
      ),
      body: Center(
        child: ConstrainedBox(
          constraints: const BoxConstraints(maxWidth: 1100),
          child: Padding(
            padding: const EdgeInsets.symmetric(vertical: 24, horizontal: 8),
            child: Row(
              children: [
                // Recents/History Panel
